        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "This project aims to increase rural smallholder farmers’ income by facilitating their engagement in commercial agriculture markets which provide them with better opportunities to increase their income and improve their livelihood and competitiveness.Phase II focuses on growth and investment in forward market linkages, strengthening the country’s commercialisation, processing and export of value-added agriculture products. It will provide financial and technical support towards increased provision of services and access to innovation for agri-businesses"
